  "title": "Delivery Driver cum Installation (Temporary)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>· Deliver and Install a wide variety of items to different addresses and through different routes</p><p>· Load, unload, prepare, inspect goods for delivery</p><p>· Operate and maintain delivery vehicle</p><p>· Assist in other ad-hoc warehouse duties when required</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>· Valid Class 3 driver’s licence with good record</p><p>· Physically Fit, able to lift load up to 20kg</p><p>· Works Monday to Saturday, 9am-6pm</p><p>· Collection and returning of 10ft lorry daily at office</p><p>· Understand Chinese will be an advantage</p>",
