    "description": "<p>Singapore Furniture focuses on providing all of our customers with quality services and well-designed office furniture, whether it’s for the Government Agencies, Multi-National Corporations(MNCs) or Home Office. We had worked with public &amp; private schools, 5-stars hotels, shipyards, restaurants, and numerous companies.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Singapore Furniture’s team of friendly and responsive people, offers additional value to their clients’ workspace, in terms of space design and planning services. We can offer advice on workspace safety and health, lighting, data &amp; voice cabling, and more.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Singapore Furniture was established in January 1964, and through the many years of experience in the furniture business, we are able to secured agreements with local &amp; overseas top manufacturers and suppliers, to</p>\n<p>provide a large selection of office furniture that is of an equally high quality and cost-effective.</p>\n<p>Moving forward, with its continuous expansion, Singapore Furniture has drawn up ambitious plans to extend its export businesses to countries in the South East Asia and United States of America.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At Singapore Furniture, we believe in making Better Life at Work!</p>",
